大，她电动车倒了很难扶起来，这时一个新疆小伙子跑上来迅速帮妈妈扶起来，妈妈向他道谢，他笑着说没事，就走掉了。所以妈妈说，也不能一棍子敲死，只是有一些人不好，影响了整个民族给人的印象", "like_count": 15, "author_name": "梨小猫", "author_id": "144b53a42b8ee0be96a3b1108c884819", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "zzl-23-29", "headline": "会计学生", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "961728822", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "961728822", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "初中的时候，校门口摆了一个切糕摊儿，大冬天的冒着热腾腾的气儿，看着眼馋就去问问，切了一小片，一称给我说50多，当时身上总共都没那么多钱。我说不要了，他不同意，不准我走了。我就搁旁边站着，也不走，但凡有人来问切糕，我就指着我称的那一片儿说，看见没，那片儿50多，问一个走一个，老板就坐不住了，急着把我赶走了😂😂😂", "like_count": 15, "author_name": "清欢", "author_id": "4bb1a09f65c2f7411ca6391283b18e03", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "liu-yuan-chu-xiao-ge-ge", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2094108369", "reply_comment_id": "961728822", "reply_root_comment_id": "961728822", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "不怕被打啊", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "刘元楚小哥哥", "author_id": "727f4ce0658f58d4ebce93a104febfae", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "kyudo_sz", "headline": "弓道练习者", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "959438620", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "959438620", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "评一下上面不要香菜那位回民老大姐。作为一名新疆人民，不是切糕诈骗的受众，就不要在那里指手画脚说“切糕诈骗”的受害者都是没问清楚的“活该”的人。删掉自己的回答只能说明心虚。我很少在知乎杠人，要是你之前遇到被我杠，只能说明你这个人够欠。", "like_count": 12, "author_name": "虞仲癸", "author_id": "b111c7b7ec4f0dce6bfd6086d9510ea1", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "yi-wei-21-24", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "987031115", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "987031115", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "五十一斤就偷着乐吧，我上次买的20块钱一两", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "艺伟", "author_id": "a4c0cc01e5441dc1a76fa0ec1952aa38", "author_is_anonymous": fals